approved for triple-negative and HR-positive breast cancer.

104
00:13:16.198 --> 00:13:20.037
Since I'm the first ADC talk in the session, I'll go over the

105
00:13:20.138 --> 00:13:24.108
major features. So SG, an antibody targeting

106
00:13:24.108 --> 00:13:28.058
the cell surface protein Trop-2. The payload

107
00:13:28.258 --> 00:13:31.518
is a topoisomerase 1 inhibitor, SN-38,

108
00:13:32.378 --> 00:13:35.518
and linked via a cleavable and

109
00:13:35.578 --> 00:13:37.658
hydrolyzable linker.

110
00:13:38.738 --> 00:13:42.698
So SG first demonstrated efficacy most

111
