113
00:13:50.418 --> 00:13:54.178
patients with heavily pretreated TNBC, that SG

114
00:13:54.198 --> 00:13:58.138
nearly doubled overall survival compared to physician's choice

115
00:13:58.538 --> 00:13:59.458
