00:26:38.470 --> 00:26:42.440
response. Because if it's important to prognosis in triple-negative breast cancer,

323
00:26:42.650 --> 00:26:45.739
the primary endpoint with pathologic complete response, which was

324
00:26:45.930 --> 00:26:49.820
30% to SG alone, and Laura published the results in

325
00:26:49.910 --> 00:26:53.710
Annals a couple of years ago. From our point of view, we

326
00:26:53.750 --> 00:26:57.210
were very pleased to be able to develop a strong translational backbone on this

327
00:26:57.270 --> 00:27:00.710
study with pre-post treatment biopsies that we could do single-cell RNA-seq,

328
00:27:01.470 --> 00:27:01.770
tumor

329
00:27:02.790 --> 00:27:03.450
whole exome

330
00:27:04.470 --> 00:27:07.890
sequencing, and then a multiplex spatial

