00:27:07.930 --> 00:27:11.390
immunofluorescence, and then really do an integrative analysis

332
00:27:11.510 --> 00:27:15.130
to try to identify the features associated with

333
00:27:15.170 --> 00:27:19.050
response and progression, in this case, really dividing

