00:43:27.258 --> 00:43:30.978
various types of therapies. Over the last 15 years or so,

617
00:43:31.078 --> 00:43:34.938
we've seen an explosion of new therapies for bladder cancer.

618
00:43:35.468 --> 00:43:38.258
And I think the thing that I want to point out is that every single one of these

619
00:43:38.278 --> 00:43:41.098
therapies actually goes after a cell surface protein. Okay?

620
00:43:41.178 --> 00:43:44.028
Whether it's our antibody drug conjugates that we're going to talk about today,

621
00:43:44.518 --> 00:43:48.288
like EV, SG, that Dr. Allison just talked about, or HER2 targeting

