00:44:39.298 --> 00:44:42.848
And just showing you a few of those, including ADCs,

637
00:44:42.918 --> 00:44:46.378
radioligands, T-cell engagers, CARs, TCR therapies.

638
00:44:46.778 --> 00:44:47.038
I think

639
00:44:48.078 --> 00:44:51.868
really the sky is out there in terms of

