00:45:40.938 --> 00:45:44.398
population. And what we saw from this trial that was published over six years ago,

655
00:45:44.518 --> 00:45:48.018
seven years ago now, was that we saw an overall response rate of 45% with a

656
00:45:48.198 --> 00:45:51.438
