00:48:03.546 --> 00:48:06.385
the difference in survival is extreme, right?

694
00:48:06.426 --> 00:48:10.226
So the patients who have nectin-4 amplifications are doing extraordinarily

695
00:48:10.246 --> 00:48:13.306
better than those without the non-amplified tumors.

696
00:48:13.346 --> 00:48:17.156
We've seen this now in our own UCSF cohort, as I think many other people in this

