707
00:48:51.826 --> 00:48:54.326
So here are the questions that we've been thinking about.

708
00:48:54.386 --> 00:48:57.546
How do bladder cancer cells actually regulate nectin-4, and can we leverage those

709
00:48:57.606 --> 00:49:00.966
mechanisms to essentially use some parlance from the immunotherapy literature?

710
00:49:01.046 --> 00:49:04.846
Can we turn our cold nectin-4 tumors into hot nectin-4

