00:49:10.966 --> 00:49:14.466
staining a TMA from Dr. Peter Black at UBC,

714
00:49:14.566 --> 00:49:18.026
that nectin-4 expression is very heterogeneous in MIBC.

715
00:49:19.026 --> 00:49:22.726
And if we take a look at the molecular subtypes of bladder cancer, what we've seen,

716
00:49:22.786 --> 00:49:26.406
whether we look at the protein level or at the mRNA level, is that there's a

